  "EAR = (1 + r/n)^n - 1 converts a nominal rate with compounding into the actual annual yield. For example, 12% compounded monthly has an EAR of 12.68%.": "EAR = 1 + r/n)n - 1 转换名义汇率,再加到实际年收益率。例如,12%的复合月收益率为12.68%。",
