  "WACC is the Weighted Average Cost of Capital. It blends the after-tax cost of debt and the cost of equity, weighted by their proportions in the capital structure. It serves as the minimum hurdle rate for projects.": "WACC是资本加权平均成本,结合债务税后成本和股本成本,按资本结构中的比例加权,作为项目的最低障碍率。",
