  "Dividend yield = Annual Dividend / Stock Price. For example, a $2.40 annual dividend on a $60 stock gives a 4% yield. It measures the income return from holding a stock.": "股息收益 = 年度股息/股价。例如,60美元股票的2.40美元年度股息收益为4%。它衡量持有股票的收入收益。",
