  "A homeowner pays $15,000 in mortgage interest this year and is in the 24% tax bracket. How much does the mortgage interest deduction save them in taxes?": "一个房主今年支付15,000美元的按揭利息,并列在24%的税项内。 抵押利息扣除能为他们节省多少税?",
