  "Fund A has a 11% return with 16% standard deviation. Fund B has an 8% return with 7% standard deviation. The risk-free rate is 3%. Which fund has the better Sharpe ratio?": "基金A的回报率为11%,标准差为16%。基金B的回报率为8%,标准差为7%。无风险率为3%。哪个基金的夏普率更好?",
