  "Fund B with a Sharpe ratio of 0.71": "基金B,夏普比率为0.71",
  "Fund A Sharpe = (11 - 3) / 16 = 0.50. Fund B Sharpe = (8 - 3) / 7 = 0.71. Fund B delivers more excess return per unit of risk, making it the better risk-adjusted choice.": "A基金=(11-3)/16=0.50。B基金=(8-3)/7=0.71。B基金为每个风险单位带来更多超额回报,从而作出更好的风险调整选择。",
  "A company is financed with 50% debt at 5% after-tax cost and 50% equity at 11% cost of equity. What is the company's WACC?": "一家公司50%的债务由5%的税后成本和50%的股本融资,11%的股本成本。 该公司的WACC是什么?",
