  "A bakery has fixed costs of $36,000/year and sells cakes for $45 each with a variable cost of $18 per cake. If they raise the price to $50, how many fewer cakes are needed to break even?": "一家面包店每年固定成本36 000美元,每家45美元的蛋糕销售,每家可变成本为每家18美元。 如果每家面包店将价格提高到50美元,那么折叠蛋糕需要少多少?",
  "100 fewer": "减少100",
  "334 fewer": "少334,少334",
  "209 fewer": "减少209",
  "500 fewer": "减少500",
  "At $45: BEP = $36,000 / ($45 - $18) = 1,334 cakes. At $50: BEP = $36,000 / ($50 - $18) = 1,125 cakes. Difference = 1,334 - 1,125 = 209 fewer cakes needed to break even.": "45美元:BEP = 36 000美元 / (45 - 18美元) = 1 334个蛋糕 . 50美元: BEP = 36 000美元 / (50 - 18美元) = 1 125个蛋糕. 差异 = 1 334 - 1 125 = 减少209个蛋糕,以达到平衡。",
  "A worker saves $300/month starting at age 25, earning 8% annually (compounded monthly) until retirement at 65 (40 years). Approximately how much will they accumulate?": "从25岁开始,每个工人每月节省300美元,年收入为8%(按月计算),直到65岁退休(40岁)。",
