  "Bank A offers 6% compounded monthly. Bank B offers 6.1% compounded annually. Which bank offers the higher effective annual rate (EAR)?": "A银行每月提供6%的复数。 B银行每年提供6.1%的复数。 哪家银行提供更高的有效年利率(EAR ) ?",
