  "Bank A EAR = (1 + 0.06/12)^12 - 1 = (1.005)^12 - 1 = 6.17%. Bank B EAR = 6.10% (annual compounding means EAR equals the stated rate). Bank A's more frequent compounding produces a higher effective rate.": "A银行的EAR=(1+0.06/12)12-1=(1.005)12-1=6.17%。B银行的EAR=6.10%(年度加工厂的EAR等于规定的费率)。A银行的更频繁的化合物产生更高的有效率。",
  "An entrepreneur evaluates a new venture with a 60% chance of $50,000 profit, 25% chance of breaking even, and 15% chance of a $30,000 loss. What is the expected value of this venture?": "企业家对一家新企业的评价是,其利润为50 000美元的60%的几率,平均突破的几率为25%,损失为30 000美元的几率为15%。 这个企业的预期价值是多少?",
  "$30,000": "30 000美元",
